description.narrative: The participation of adolescents and youth was promoted and their capacities to protect themselves increased with a continued investment in life-skills education through a diversification of interventions and additional partnerships. Of particular importance, a renewed investment in innovations and a partnership formalized with the Muslim Algerian Scouts, key organization in capacity to reach out to the most deprived regions of the country. Four (4) youth-friendly houses projects were selected as model for effective youth participation in the design and the management of the center's activities. | Status:Constrained | As-of Date:29/12/2019
